title: Hidden Jewel..Minutes away from Addisons. Close To Major Highways
posting_body: ["Hidden jewel in Carrollton steps away from Addison's best dining, shopping, entertainment, and night life.", 'After all Addison has the most restaurants per square mile in the Dallas/Ft. Worth area.', 'Nestled in a quiet Carrollton residential neighborhood.', 'Quiet living and relaxation are made easy with our large floor plans and a large secluded 2 level pool with waterfall.', 'We are conveniently located in Carrollton just minutes away from IH-635, 190 (George Bush Tollway) and the North Dallas Tollway.', 'Premium townhomes available in any floorplan located feet from the water.', 'The amazing views from every window in your home will amaze all your friends and guest.', 'We have plenty to offer to everyone.', 'If you are single, Beltline Rd. features the best pubs, bars, and entertainment.', 'If you are a doggie lover, we offer private fenced back yards.', 'What a great bonus for your pet!', 'If you are a family unit, Farmers Branch/Carrollton ISD!', 'Country Place Elementary is located walking distance offering the best public education for your child.', 'Country Place elementary is a exemplary campus with yearly awards and higher test ratings above district and state average.', 'If your car is your best asset, we offer single car garages with remote access', 'Breathtaking views of Lake*', 'Spacious 1 bedroom / den and 2 bedroom floor plans', 'Townhomes include a garage, covered parking or a carport and private fenced yards*', 'Ceramic tile entries', 'Large kitchens with ceramic tile, ice makers and self cleaning ovens', 'Ceiling fans with light fixtures', 'Full size washer / dryer connections', 'Onsite laundry facility', 'Extra storage', 'Secluded 2 level pool with waterfall', 'Large pets welcome (No aggressive breeds)', 'Please call Desiree at', 'show contact info', 'Mention ad D 190', 'DASH Apartment Locators']
